Nissan Plant in Portugal May Make Other Components, Publico Says

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-02-14T08:51:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/nissan-s-battery-plant-in-portugal-may-make-other-components-publico-says.html
Nissan Motor Co.’s electric car
battery factory in Portugal may produce other components at a
later stage, Publico reported, citing Nissan Executive Vice
President  Carlos Tavares .  If the results of the battery plant in Cacia, northern
Portugal, meet expectations then there are other “possible
opportunities,” Tavares said, according to Publico.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joao Lima at 
 jlima1@bloomberg.net  